The '''Dalos Peninsula''' was the site of the [[Verkuylian BactaCo]]'s corporate headquarters on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Verkuyl]]. Much of the peninsula was used for the housing of both the workers and residents of the planet in the settlement of [[Headquarters]].

